Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.13,0:01:56.97,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}湧上心頭的 感動
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.89,0:02:07.06,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}沐浴著湛藍的陽光
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.92,0:02:11.42,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}你迎風前行的身姿
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.74,0:02:18.10,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}讓我陶醉時 目光相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.22,0:02:22.96,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}我們齊聲歡笑
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.81,0:02:30.23,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}就像那 小小漩渦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.10,0:02:37.01,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,1000)\an3}無論何時 都想揮動雙手的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.89,0:02:41.30,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}確實是 曾經
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.69,0:02:46.83,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}與你同在的印記
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.58,0:02:51.18,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}永遠如 小小漩渦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.59,0:03:00.97,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}我們的前方 道路在延伸
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.39,0:03:09.70,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}攀上 下一個陡坡後
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.49,0:03:14.46,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,1000)}我們再相見吧
